laboratory_examinations.findings: The central cardiac shadow with visible methyl methacrylate struts.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Overall, the patient exhibits good growth, with no apparent interference from the alloplastic struts.

laboratory_examinations.findings: Four struts of methyl methacrylate covered with Marlex mesh, wired to the ribs to reconstruct the sternal defect.
Incorporation of struts in the anterior chest wall without migration or fracture.
